Title: Reply to "A note on the innocuous implications of a minimum length in  quantum gravity" by P.H. Frampton
Authors: Cosimo Bambi and Katherine Freese
Abstract: We reply to the comment "A note on the innocuous implications of a minimum length in quantum gravity" by P.H. Frampton [Class. Quantum Grav. 26 (2009) 018001, arXiv:arXiv:0808.0283] on our paper "Dangerous implications of a minimum length in quantum gravity" [Class. Quantum Grav. 25 (2008) 195013, arXiv:0803.0749].
